# Michvi — Digital Governance Advisory Platform

Independent governance advisory focused on signal integrity, identity continuity, consent architecture, and structural accountability across analytics and AI-driven systems.

## Stack
- Next.js (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Custom dataLayer (governance-first)

## Deployment
- Vercel (staging + production)

## Note
This repository contains public-facing architecture only.  
Core governance logic and analytical frameworks are not exposed.
